		<h2>The Docket Method</h2>

		<p>The purpose of the docket method is to keep you focused and working on your three most important tasks of the day.
			One of the biggest killers of productivity are distractions.  This system is designed to enable you to quickly deal with distractions and get back to work.
		</p>
	</div>
